<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.5.2">
<l>kōḷari yiṉṉuruvaṅ koṇṭavu ṇaṉuṭalam kuruti kuḻampiyeḻak kūruki rālkuṭaivāy</l>
<l>mīḷava vaṉmakaṉai meymmaiko ḷakkaruti mēlaiya mararpati mikkuve kuṇṭuvarak</l>
<l>kāḷanaṉ mēkamavai kalloṭu kālpoḻiyak karuti varaikkuṭaiyāk kālikaḷ kāppavaṉē</l>
<l>yāḷave ṉakkorukā lāṭuka ceṅkīrai yāyarkaḷ pōrēṟē yāṭuka vāṭukavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With the form of a murderous lion, you are the one who scoops out the blood</l>
<l rend="indent">of the Asura’s body with [your] sharp claws so that [it] spurts out [and] shoots up,</l>
<l>having intended for the truth to be grasped and so that his son would be liberated.</l>
<l>When the Lord of the immortals above came greatly enraged,</l>
<l rend="indent">intending for those abundant black clouds to pour forth stones along with pebbles,</l>
<l>you are the one who protected the cows with a mountain as an umbrella!</l>
<l>Lord, dance one time for me! Battle bull of the cowherds, dance the Ceṅkīrai, please dance!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
